node.text: Honored to spend time with #Tokyo2020 athletes, @mariahduran_, @alicedearingx, @erica.sully and @briantmpr, who inspire us with their acts of good. Not only are they amazing competitors, they are also committed to serving others by stepping up for equality and inclusion, and for their communities. Special thanks to @nastialiukin and @guskenworthy for hosting such an important conversation - it is one you don't want to miss! Check out the Athletes for Good Fund panel through our link in bio. #LeadWithLove #Tokyo2020 #StrongerTogether
